metadata.name: Time, Time...
metadata.description:
La Croix de Berny, Antony
2021

I took this picture in 2021 on a Mamiya DSX 1000, using an Ilford HP5 400 film.


Lines, shapes, lights, shadows has always found a way to amaze me, so I do my best to capture the beautiful world with a unique eye !
Each one of these photos represents a moment in time where all these components have aligned to form a powerful composition !
